task.summary: Added a text file called "dictionary.txt" with 8000+ words. Created a Dictionary class to manipulate this file, able to search for a word in the dictionary and indicating if it exists or not. main.cpp modified with small test of dictionary.

Created LetterTile class, that stores a string indicating the letter that represents, the amount of tiles for this letter available and the score. Created GameDeck class that reads from a new text file in CSV format. It reads all the LetterTiles that has to created for the game and adds it to a Linked List.

On GameDeck class, created giveRandomLetter function. Returns a letter in a random position obtained from srand. Takes in consideration the total amount of letters remaining (100 at the start of the program). This function may be modified in the future. Reorganized project directories. Created Objects directory that stores Dictionary, GameDeck and LetterTile.

Finished internal documentation of every class created at the moment. Generated HTML file with Doxygen Modified giveRandomLetter() method in GameDeck class. Deleted redundant or unnecessary validations.
Added Doxyfile (doxygen config file) and html directory created by doxygen.
Separated code in Objects directory in a .hpp file containing the class declaration and a .cpp file containing the code implementation.
GameDeck now contains an array of LetterTiles instead of a Linked List.
Created Player.hpp and its basic methods and attributes.
Added methods to add and delete LetterTiles from playerDeck
Player methods are now in player.cpp
Included a GameDeck attribute in Board. Changed directories names.
Created test in main for player methods
